text: Aušra Gudeliūnaitė (born 5 September 1963) is a Lithuanian rowing coxswain. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:Lithuanian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Soviet Union Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vilnius Category:Coxswains (rowing)
